              a(href='#') @code_barbarian
            li.hidden-md.hidden-lg
              a(href='#') TCB Github
            li.hidden-md.hidden-lg
              a(href='#') TCB Facebook


    div.container
      div.col-lg-9.post-text
        .row
          .title-byline-container 
            h1.post-title How to Code Like A Bawse
            p.byline by Val Karpov
          .source-code-button
            .btn.btn-orange.btn-block
              i.glyphicon.glyphicon-heart
              | Code for this Post

        .row.post-body-text-container
          .col-lg-12
            p.post-paragraph
              | Mongoose right now doesn't run validators on calls to Model.update(). 
              | I've found often that its more elegant and performant to call update() 
              | directly instead of loading the document, modifying it, and then 
              | saving it. Mongoose should have better support for this paradigm in the future.

      div.col-lg-3.right-bar
        h2 Search
        | !{content}